ALL THE WAY

Our new showreel piece incorporating a small but special selection of our drone, gimbal and tracking work over the last 3 years.

Shot using a variety of different cameras and platforms including DJI Inspire 2 X5s and X7, Freefly Alta 8 and Kopterworx Hammer X8 with RED Epic 6k, RED Helium 8k, RED Weapon 8k, RED Gemini 5k and Arri Alexa Mini.

A massive thank you to all our operators and clients who travel allover the world to help us capture the stunning content in this reel.

Get in touch: hello@fleye.co.uk
